{"tid":38526,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Android Pay 終於殺到日本","createTime":"2016-12-14T03:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T14:15:56.000Z","uid":731,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c638a12812b0b1794824dbfdb494ee48c3c0dcd8","tid":38526,"uid":731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:40:23.000Z","msg":"聖誕新年假期，相信有不少網友會去日本旅行渡假，如果你是 Android 手機用戶，有好消息話你知，Google 昨日宣佈 Android Pay 登陸日本。Google 和當地電子商貿龍頭 Rakuten 合作，使用對方的 Rakuten Edy 系統，包括 Family Mart、Apita、Lawson、OK 便利店、Bic Camera、Yodobashi Camera、麥當勞、汽水自動販賣機等商號使用。<br />\n<br />\n首階段支持 Android Pay 的日本商店就已經有超過 47 萬間，而且還支援 Rakuten 的 Super Points 計劃。Google 表示稍後將會和日本的 FeliCa 網絡合作，陸續增加 eMoney 服務，明年更會開始增加 Visa、MasterCard 和東京三菱銀行等的傳統付款方式。相比起個半月前在日本推出的 Apple Pay 只支援 iPhone 7 和 7 Plus，Android Pay 的好處是支援手機的種類更多，大部份 Android 4.4.4 或以上系統的手機都可以使用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4247/207208/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4247%2F207208%2F1%2F&d=yTAR3Yr94ElvWOauvY8tmAv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=2303e224\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4247/207208/1/</a>"},{"pid":"590f1cb6a3c7e9e026cbe031431cf5da2dca86ac","tid":38526,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:40:44.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"63a0080c9922f3b8821bfbce678ec2720d79c66d","tid":38526,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:40:49.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"26ddd176581b2db98910d6b4fa4171d00f86a776","tid":38526,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748e65962c9770bba65dd8f848ad07ba7aa08efb","tid":38526,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307409f4f102d28f8238409ee5bdacc3